&gt; Ni a hte kasuwa don sabon bike (kasance ba tare da na &#39;yan shekaru). &gt; Biyu main kekuna Ina neman a tsanani ne&gt; A Kawasaki Virago 535 da Honda Shadow VLX 583.&gt; Ina jingina zuwa ga Kawasaki domin ta shaft drive, da Honda ne Sarkar. &gt; Assurance a Fla. Ne mafi m fiye da na yi tunani, saboda haka ina zama a cikin wannan&gt; ikon range.
Godiya a gaba ga wani ra&#39;ayin da aka kuma ko irin abubuwan
A abokina (wanda ke yiwuwa karanta wannan a yanzu) kamar sayi wani sabon Kawasaki Virago 750.
Bayan jawabin 1-2 hours sosai marigayi daya chilly maraice kallon shi fafitikar da kusoshi (ya cire dama fegi, sassauta da birki feda, &amp; c. &amp; C.)
Na kyakkyawa da yawa yanke shawarar ba a samu irin wannan samfurin sai dai idan ya ko wani so ya canja man / tace a gare ni.
Idan aka kwatanta da 5-minti canji da aka amfani da su domin Honda, wannan shi ne kawai zane aibi / dubawa a idanuna.
